For a node at index i (0-based indexing):

parent = (i-1)/2;
leftChild = 2*i + 1;
rightChild = 2*i + 2;

Example:

arr = [2,4,5,10,8]

Represents:

        2
      /   \
     4     5
    / \
   10  8
Min Heap Property

Every parent ≤ children

        2
      /   \
     4     5
    / \
   10  8

Valid Min Heap ✅

Max Heap Property

Every parent ≥ children

        10
      /    \
     8      5

Valid Max Heap ✅


